## CHANGE REQUEST PROTOCOL

When requirements change AFTER BRD is approved:

```
CHANGE REQUEST — [CR-001]
Date: [YYYY-MM-DD]
Requested by: [Client/Sagar]
Description: [What is changing]
Reason: [Why]
Impact Assessment:
  - Scope: [Added/removed/changed features]
  - Timeline: [+/- X days/weeks]
  - Effort: [+/- X story points]
  - Risk: [Any new risks introduced]
  - Modules affected: [List]
Decision: APPROVED / REJECTED / DEFERRED
Approved by: Sagar
BRD Version: [Bump to 1.1, 1.2, etc.]
```

Update BRD version when approved. Notify all department heads via STATUS.md.

